import React from "react";
const TravelAgencies = () => {
    return 
    return <>
    <CommonSection title={"All Pharmacies"} />
    <section>
        <Container>
            <Row>
                <SearchBar />
            </Row>
        </Container>
    </section>
    <section>
        <Container>
            <Row>
                {
                    pharmacieData?.map(location => <Col lg="3" key={location.id}> <LocationCard location={location} /></Col>)

                }
            </Row>
        </Container>
    </section>
    </>
};
export default TravelAgencies;
